    "Downstream TasksThe pretrained generator model explained in the previous section can be fine-tuned on a wide range of downstream tasks.",
    "As case studies in this paper, we have selected tasks including semantic segmentation of nanoparticles, denoising, noise & background removal, and super-resolution in high-resolution TEM images.Semantic segmentation involves labeling each pixel of an image with a corresponding class of what is being represented.",
